        {
            "title": "國際｜英王查爾斯美國國會演說 籲摒棄孤立主義捍衛英美同盟",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"國際｜英王查爾斯美國國會演說 籲摒棄孤立主義捍衛英美同盟\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">國際｜英王<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"查爾斯\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:查爾斯;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/查爾斯\">查爾斯</a>美國國會演說 籲摒棄孤立主義捍衛英美同盟</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">英國國王查爾斯三世近日展開為期四天的訪美行程，並於第二天前往國會山莊向美國國會聯席會議發表講話。在演說中，查爾斯三世展現出罕見且尖銳的外交姿態，公開呼籲美國應繼續保持全球領導地位，全力支持烏克蘭及北大西洋公約組織（NATO），並嚴正敦促美國人民抵制日益抬頭的孤立主義誘惑。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他在副總統范斯（JD Vance）與眾議院議長約翰遜（Mike Johnson）的注視下強調，英美同盟應與歐洲及英聯邦夥伴併肩作戰，捍衛共同價值觀，並無視那些要求國家日益封閉、僅關注自身利益的噪音。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-7cfd6578-e9a6-3a89-aca9-6caf3c775d69-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">此次演說背景正值英美關係陷入數十年來的冰點。由於美國總統特朗普與英國首相施紀賢（Keir Starmer）近期因伊朗戰爭及川普威脅吞併格陵蘭等議題產生嚴重分歧。在這種緊張氛圍下，查爾斯三世此行扮演了極其重要的外交調解角色。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">儘管其演說措辭經過外交修飾，但在支持北約、援助烏克蘭及保護環境等議題上的強硬表態，仍被外界普遍解讀為對特朗普政府現行政策的隱晦批評與制衡。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">查爾斯三世在講話中特別提及兩國深厚的歷史淵源，笑言雖然雙方自1776年美國獨立革命以來並非總是意見一致，但兩國在文化、宗教及立國原則上的聯繫始終牢固。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B-%E8%8B%B1%E7%8E%8B%E6%9F%A5%E7%88%BE%E6%96%AF%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E6%BC%94%E8%AA%AA-%E7%B1%B2%E6%91%92%E6%A3%84%E5%AD%A4%E7%AB%8B%E4%B8%BB%E7%BE%A9%E6%8D%8D%E8%A1%9B%E8%8B%B1%E7%BE%8E%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F-060253958.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-29 14:10:41",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "特斯拉將在國際市場推出全自動駕駛軟體",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.130ucTWhmOBTs8AJXOEJw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEA9Q076_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com- <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"特斯拉\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:特斯拉;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/特斯拉\">特斯拉</a> (NASDAQ:TSLA) 週二表示,計劃在美國推出針對配備HW3硬體車輛的V14 Lite版本後,將其全自動駕駛(FSD)軟體擴展至更多國際市場。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該公司表示,此次更新旨在確保HW3車輛的車主能夠持續獲得軟體支援,即使在推出更新硬體版本的情況下也是如此。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span><span><span><span>特斯拉</span></span></span></span>補充說,FSD V14 Lite的國際部署將取決於多項因素,包括完成技術驗證、針對特定地區的調整,以及獲得必要的監管批准。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-265bec37-ad55-3cec-88ed-2c5c43df4bd5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因此,該公司表示無法為全球市場的推出提供明確的時間表,但將在達成各項里程碑時陸續提供更新資訊。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">FSD是特斯拉軟體驅動策略的關鍵組成部分,一直是其提升自動駕駛能力並透過軟體升級產生經常性收入的核心努力,儘管該系統在多個地區仍面臨監管審查。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
